summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Seattle Legislative Department, authorizing acceptance of a grant from the Skagit Environmental Endowment Commission for financial assistance to support cataloging, digitizing, and making available for research photographic images documenting the history, development, and environment of the Upper Skagit Watershed; and making a reimbursable appropriation from the General Fund therefor, all by a three-fourths vote of the City Council.
